  "instructions": [
    "Heat the olive oil in a large skillet over medium heat.",
    "Add the diced onion and minced garlic, cooking until softened, about 5 minutes.",
    "Stir in the haricot beans and lemon juice. Cover and simmer for 10-15 minutes or until tender.",
    "Drizzle balsamic vinegar evenly over the top and stir to combine.",
    "Season with smoked paprika, salt, and pepper to taste.",
    "Serve hot as a side dish."
